# Auth0 JS Features

## Responsibilities
- Use official Auth0 SDK; avoid custom token/session storage.
- Implement login/logout, user, token, RBAC, social, MFA.

## Triggers
- auth0-features
- auth0-setup

## Patterns (sketch)
```js
// login
await auth0Client.loginWithRedirect();
// user
const user = await auth0Client.getUser();
// token
const token = await auth0Client.getTokenSilently();
```

